SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT DISTINCT KUNDEN.Ort from KUNDEN WITH(NOLOCK) where KUNDEN.Ebene1=:1 and KUNDEN.Ebene2=:2 and KUNDEN.Ebene3=:3 and KUNDEN.Ebene4=:4 ORDER BY KUNDEN.Ort
SELECT DISTINCT Strasse FROM KUNDEN WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Ebene1=:1 AND Ebene2=:2 AND Ebene3=:3 AND Ebene4=:4 AND Strasse >' ' ORDER BY Strasse

SELECT DISTINCT KUNDEN.Telefon, KUNDEN.Matchcode FROM KUNDEN WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE KUNDEN.Telefon >'' AND KUNDEN.Ebene1=:1 AND KUNDEN.Ebene2=:2 AND KUNDEN.Ebene3=:3 AND KUNDEN.Ebene4=:4 ORDER BY KUNDEN.Telefon

SELECT KONTAKTPERSON.Name, KONTAKTPERSON.Vorname, KONTAKTPERSON.Abteilung, KONTAKTPERSON.Kunden_Nr FROM KONTAKTPERSON WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE KONTAKTPERSON.Name >'' AND KONTAKTPERSON.Ebene1=:1 and KONTAKTPERSON.Ebene2=:2 and KONTAKTPERSON.Ebene3=:3 and KONTAKTPERSON.Ebene4=:4 ORDER BY KONTAKTPERSON.Name

SELECT GERAETE.IDNR, GERAETE.Serien_Nr, GERAETE.ModellBezeichnung, GERAETE.Rechnungsempfnger from GERAETE with(NOLOCK) where GERAETE.Ebene1=:1 and GERAETE.Ebene2=:2 and GERAETE.Ebene3=:3 and GERAETE.Ebene4=:4
